# WINET Lab Website Project Overview

This is the official website for the Wireless Intelligence and Networked Things Laboratory (WINET) at City University of Hong Kong.

## Project Structure
- [index.html](mdc:index.html): Main entry point of the website
- [styles.css](mdc:styles.css): Global styles for the website
- [script.js](mdc:script.js): Main JavaScript functionality
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies

## Complete File Structure
```
JC-Lab-Modernism.io/
├── .cursor/                    # Cursor IDE configuration
│   └── rules/                  # Project rules and guidelines
├── assets/                     # Static assets
│   └── slides/                 # Presentation slides
├── data/                       # Project data
│   ├── people/                 # Team member information
